§ 10. SAFETY-CRITICAL APPLICATIONS

  10.1 This Software has not been evaluated, tested, or certified for use in
       any safety-critical, life-critical, or high-consequence environment.
       You are expressly advised NOT to deploy this Software in:

         (a) Medical devices, diagnostic systems, or life-support systems;
         (b) Aviation, aerospace, or autonomous vehicle control systems;
         (c) Nuclear facility management or radiation control systems;
         (d) Critical infrastructure, power grid, or water treatment systems;
         (e) Military or defense applications;
         (f) Any environment where software failure could reasonably result
             in injury, death, significant property damage, or environmental
             harm.

  10.2 If you deploy the Software in any context listed in § 10.1, you do so
       entirely at your own risk and liability. The Neuro Project Contributors
       expressly disclaim all liability for such deployments to the maximum
       extent permitted by applicable law.

